Package com.googlecode.objectify

Interface Summary
Objectify This interface is similar to DatastoreService, except that instead of working with Entity you work with real typed objects.
OPreparedQuery<T> This interface mimics the GAE PreparedQuery interface, but instead of iterating through Entity objects, it iterates through your typesafe objects.
 

Class Summary
DatastoreTimeoutRetryProxy A dynamic proxy that catches DatastoreTimeoutException and retries the action up to a specified number of times.
EntityMetadata<T> Everything you need to know about mapping between Datastore Entity objects and typed entity objects.
ObjectifyFactory Factory which allows us to construct implementations of the Objectify interface.
ObjectifyImpl Implementation of the Objectify interface.
ObjectifyService This is a simple container for a single static instance of ObjectifyFactory.
OKey<T> This is a typesafe version of the Key object.
OPreparedQueryImpl<T> Implementation of the ObjPreparedQuery interface.
OQuery<T> This is similar to the datastore Query object, but better understands real class objects - it allows you to filter and sort by the key field normally.
